## Docker Usage

Build and run TPTT with Docker:

```bash
# Build the image
docker build -t tptt .

# Run training (with GPU support)
docker run -it --gpus all \
  -v $(pwd)/data:/data \
  -v $(pwd)/outputs:/outputs \
  tptt python -m train \
    --model_name "meta-llama/Llama-3.2-1B" \
    --method delta_rule \
    --mag_weight 0.5

```

For more details, see the Dockerfile.

